data.description: A truly charming property with its lovely brick exterior, spacious interior, and picturesque surroundings. The combination of historic wooden accents and modern amenities create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The courtyard and backyard are perfect spaces for relaxation and entertaining. And the proximity to Chattanooga, Atlanta, and Birmingham adds to the appeal, offering both convenience and the allure of nearby urban centers. It is a wonderful opportunity for anyone looking for a blend of classic charm and modern comfort in a downtown setting.
